2 Hours Ago The NAF Director of Public Relations and Information, Air Commodore Gabkwet Edward, stated this in a release on Friday. He said, "An air crash involving a @NigAirForce aircraft occurred this evening near the Kaduna International Airport. The immediate cause of the crash is still being ascertained. More details to follow soon."  An air crash involving a @NigAirForce aircraft occurred this evening near the Kaduna International Airport. The immediate cause of the crash is still being ascertained. More details to follow soon.Edward GabkwetAir CommodoreDirector of Public Relations and Information21/5/21 pic.twitter.com/N01V2M6qUc 